{"tid":499403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"茶餐廳舐匙取糖 食客遭毆命危","createTime":"2017-12-14T18:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T07:57:27.000Z","uid":36995,"like":251,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d12db81ebda2b5cd8aada35013a3ea5e51be77","tid":499403,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T18:07:46.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】秀茂坪順天邨發生傷人案。一名男子昨在邨內「冬菇亭」茶餐廳吃早餐時，被指用剛舐過的匙羹在糖罌取糖，惹來同枱食客斥責不衛生，雙方爆發罵戰，繼而大打出手，取糖者最終被打至昏迷，送院命危，涉案男子則被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n同枱口角變單挑<br />\n<br />\n男傷者姓黃，58歲，頭部重傷，送院經搶救後轉往深切治療部，情况危殆。被捕男子姓梁，46歲，涉嫌傷人，被帶署扣查。昨晚約8時，梁被押返順安邨寓所搜證，其間探員檢走梁犯案時所穿衣服帶署化驗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後腦着地昏迷送院<br />\n<br />\n據悉，黃為順天邨居民，梁則居於毗鄰的順安邨，兩人不時光顧順天邨天權樓對開茶餐廳，但並不相識。消息稱，昨晨約10時，黃及梁分別到該茶餐廳吃早餐，同坐一枱，其間黃用隨熱飲奉上的匙羹，從糖罌取砂糖放入熱飲，攪動一輪後，疑試味發現不夠甜，想再加糖，但因見匙羹沾濕，遂用舌頭將匙羹舐乾，再插入糖罌取糖，此舉引來同枱的梁不滿，斥其不衛生，黃聞言不悅反駁，雙方爆發罵戰。<br />\n<br />\n兩人吵至面紅耳熱，走出茶餐廳外單挑，黃不敵，被梁擊倒，更後腦着地重傷昏迷，街坊見狀報警，梁心知闖禍，即離開，黃則由救護車送院。警員其後於順天邨停車場拘捕梁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20151011/s00002/1444499601270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151011%2Fs00002%2F1444499601270&d=QityVE64U90TG%2BhHdk7iNTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2d5eb9cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151011%2Fs00002%2F1444499601270&h=c72b17be\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20151011/s00002/1444499601270</a>"},{"pid":"e08659010419025f3598f072a18ff9681aa844b9","tid":499403,"uid":61954,"like":364,"dislike":1,"score":363,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T18:09:02.000Z","msg":"打得好！"},{"pid":"78cedddaddc821cd593ff53b4e4a734403f05675","tid":499403,"uid":28563,"like":277,"dislike":6,"score":271,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T18:09:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛又貼舊聞洗板轉移視線<br />\n大家唔好回post，比個post沉底，多謝合作<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"561ebc418b8b68ab72b7f9a6e61b9beb5469b19b","tid":499403,"uid":36995,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T18:11:16.000Z","msg":"昨晨十時許，黃前往茶餐廳與梁「搭枱」食早餐，起初相安無事。現場消息稱，黃要了一杯熱奶茶，並落糖調甜度，而糖罐內有一支不銹鋼公用匙羹，黃用自己杯內的匙羹加糖攪拌後，順勢放入口「舔乾淨」，再直接插落糖罐內舀沙糖，同枱的梁目睹情況，不滿其行徑有欠衞生，遂出言斥責黃無品(嘩！都好驚啫，既然係熟客，此行為應該行之以久；咁咪好多客食左佢口水尾都唔知)，雙方發生爭執，有人感「冇面」(佢冇面啫！其他人食左佢口水尾可能冇命喎)，怒吼：「你同我出嚟隻揪！」梁回應：「好呀！等我埋單先！你出面等我！」<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者稱，兩人在茶餐廳外「決鬥」，有人「起飛腳」踢向梁，梁不甘示弱還擊，黃被人一個勾拳擊中小腹打倒褪兩步，復衝前圖反擊，卻再中至少兩拳，失平衡倒地，懷疑頭部撼地昏迷不醒，姓陳（六十六歲）茶餐廳男負責人見狀報警求助。街坊指，梁見出事，即時上前慰問，「喂！你有冇事呀？」但黃毫無反應，遂在茶餐廳留下聯絡電話，先行離開現場。"},{"pid":"32c3b1f091083fbe56a54f49a1b7fdfc742eea8b","tid":499403,"uid":50719,"like":120,"dislike":0,"score":120,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"Old news扮新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個阿伯死左丫嘛"},{"pid":"055be22ad52629f75fef8f8883f2fcc8f811c020","tid":499403,"uid":98386,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T18:48:34.000Z","msg":"小小事搞到咁大都係因一時衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fd88055c9ff51896a8a435a0515e04ffea069d","tid":499403,"uid":74858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T21:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606674c7d3ee8f9e949487a381bf7c5f13807d19","tid":499403,"uid":33808,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T21:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打得好，不過下次咪咁激動啦"},{"pid":"ab40ce882ad8f7167c31e9e68875d6d738329cee","tid":499403,"uid":128603,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T21:36:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F&d=QityVE64U90TG%2BhHdk7iNTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2768090f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F&h=96ff67f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/</a><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">20151011</span>/s00002/1444499601270"},{"pid":"730a2bc64920fc52401c07137609bff0c1275e51","tid":499403,"uid":64850,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T21:47:04.000Z","msg":"怕且下次隻抽都要簽定生死狀"},{"pid":"9258aee50428fb463f42ae2d7de0ff24b4d7f6a6","tid":499403,"uid":47674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T22:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f351c43d9b90e0e50e98c0b8196a13ae189d87de","tid":499403,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T22:44:12.000Z","msg":"廢老最後比人收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c863450936f494966ab32dd1a30f2fdcb109290","tid":4994